         <div xml:id="alalal-i91830"><!-- l4d40dt1 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-i91830-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i91830-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="18"/>DIV1IS10 TEXTUS,
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i91830-d1e108">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="19"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-i91830-Qd1e112"> Nunc superest de cognatione, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="20"/>In istis tribus distinctionibus queritur
<lb ed="#Bf" n="21"/>de impedimento proveniente ex vicini-
<cb ed="#Bf" n="c"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="22"/>fate cognationis : et ideo hic primo
<lb ed="#Bf" n="23"/>agit de cognatione carnali. Secundo,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="24"/>de affinitate, scilicet in distinct. XLI.
<lb ed="#Bf" n="25"/>Et tertio, de cognatione spirituali, 
sci<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="26"/>licet in distinct. XLII. Quarto, de 
cogna<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="27"/>tione legali, ibi, Dist. XLU, D, <quote xml:id="alalal-i91830-Qd1e134"> Quod
<lb ed="#Bf" n="28"/>autem spirituales vel adoptivi filii, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i91830-d1e140">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="29"/>Adhuc ita distinctio dividitur in tres
<lb ed="#Bf" n="30"/>partes. Primo queritur, In quot gradi-
<pb ed="#Bf" n="443"/>
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="1"/>bus licet alicui conjungi 
matrimoniali<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="2"/>ter ? Secundo, Reddit causam quare in
<lb ed="#Bf" n="3"/>tot, ibi, C, $1: <quote xml:id="alalal-i91830-Qd1e157"> Quare vero sex 
gra<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="4"/>dus computet, Isidorus, etc. </quote> Tertio,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="5"/>Objicit quaedam et solvit, ibi, C, ยง 2:
<lb ed="#Bf" n="6"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-i91830-Qd1e166"> His autem occurrit, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i91830-d1e169">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="7"/>In prima sunt duo capitula. In primo
<lb ed="#Bf" n="8"/>ostenditur in quot gradibus attenditur
<lb ed="#Bf" n="9"/>matrimonialis copula. In secundo, 
Osten<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="10"/>dit dupheem modum, Isidori seilicet,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="11"/>et aliorum, qualiter illi gradus sunt 
com<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="12"/>putandi, ibi, B, <quote xml:id="alalal-i91830-Qd1e184"> Quomodo autem 
gra<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="13"/>dus consanguinitatis, etc. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
